{"tid":113502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日就係財委會, 局長加薪12.4%, 一個post都無!!","createTime":"2017-02-09T04:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T08:49:04.000Z","uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6f7037c01742a540ce3d2031d1aa07e2ad603e","tid":113502,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"建議<br />\n4.6 經考慮所有因素後，獨立委員會建議第五屆特區<span style=\"color: blue;\">政府各局<br />\n長</span>的<span style=\"color: red;\">現金薪酬應調高<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12.4%</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，增幅相等於2012至2016年期間丙類消費<br />\n物價指數的累積變動（2016年的幅度預計為2.5%），即每年由<br />\n3,577,380元增至4,021,200元，或每月由298,115元增至335,100元。<br />\n<br />\nSource<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr16-17/chinese/fc/fc/papers/f16-80c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr16-17%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Ffc%2Fpapers%2Ff16-80c.pdf&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=74d03626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr16-17/chinese/fc/fc/papers/f16-80c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"ce9a7c0d1c842fe57b82a24d301eaaffe18b9566","tid":113502,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:37:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c18c673f52147d1683fe91055a8c133896d16b9","tid":113502,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"貼番出來等大家回憶下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iu1uUDkXTtY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIu1uUDkXTtY&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=2258bfcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iu1uUDkXTtY</a>"},{"pid":"e0fbd28e